videos.description: Luka Doncic frantically alerts officials that the rim is tilted after he nails a step-back 3-pointer, and Boban Marjanovic attempts to fix it.

videos.description: Luka Doncic drives to the basket and arcs a high lob to Dwight Powell for the massive one-handed dunk.

videos.headline: Luka lobs to Powell for the huge finish

videos.description: Luka crosses his defender over and speeds to the basket to hammer home a vicious one-handed slam in Andre Drummond's face.
